nodes.text: Glute was a male Crolute criminal with extensive cybernetics. He was affiliated with the Razorclaw Gang, but fell out of favor with the gang's leader. Glute was hired by Republic Intelligence agent Raz Fellidrone to capture Jenza, sister of Count Dooku. Asajj Ventress, Sith apprentice to Dooku, searched for Glute, but the Crolute was killed by Fellidrone before she could learn anything from him.
